	<div class="comment comment-odd" id="comment-102355764">
		<div class="comment-content" id="comment-102355764-content">
			
			<span id="comment-102355764-content"><p>On the lack of customization in Outlook and other MS user apps:</p>

<p>I think its because the MS developers are too 1337 to understand what the adman David Oglivy understood: "The consumer is not a moron. She is your wife."</p>

<p>I wish the MS UI designers would stop trying to make their lives easier by taking away power from the users.</p>

<p>(End of rant.)</p></span>
		</div>
